  "detailed_description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enter The Fight World</h2></strong><br>Embark on an immersive journey through the remnants of a world shattered by catastrophe in this gripping survival adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931270/extras/325ce1b83f117b5bc5737ea26b00cd76.avif?t=1730437576\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931270/extras/e7188a87915053e19204d243fb840522.avif?t=1730437576\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><br>  <strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Scavenge and Survive</h2></strong><br><br>As one of the few remaining survivors, scavenge for resources amidst desolate landscapes and crumbling cities while evading hostile factions and the relentless undead.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931270/extras/abf149ebcaa24ed875b5dcaa09bb0e8f.poster.avif?t=1730437576\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931270/extras/abf149ebcaa24ed875b5dcaa09bb0e8f.webm?t=1730437576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931270/extras/abf149ebcaa24ed875b5dcaa09bb0e8f.mp4?t=1730437576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931270/extras/cc4365e75d4a301b1fbd8a5f05fd9a3a.poster.avif?t=1730437576\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931270/extras/cc4365e75d4a301b1fbd8a5f05fd9a3a.webm?t=1730437576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931270/extras/cc4365e75d4a301b1fbd8a5f05fd9a3a.mp4?t=1730437576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>  <strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Uncover the Mysteries</h2></strong><br><br>Uncover the mysteries of the apocalypse and forge alliances with fellow survivors to rebuild civilization from the ashes. But be warned, every decision carries weight in this unforgiving world where danger lurks around every corner.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931270/extras/5759670e227cc2014f09e2c8d85f9aa5.avif?t=1730437576\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><br> <strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shape Humanity's Fate  </h2></strong><br><br>Will you rise above the chaos and carve out a new future for humanity, or will you succumb to the despair of the wasteland? Your fate awaits in this captivating post-apocalyptic experience.",
